{"tid":1470611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"活學活用政府官腔－語錄集中區","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T02:26:17.000Z","uid":49833,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc30eafaa16151e4f47568baf1ea697bfdcaa97","tid":1470611,"uid":49833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:01:17.000Z","msg":"原po喺到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1470112/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1470112/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n根據巴打嘅整合，我整左幾幅圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BNRDVmK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBNRDVmK.png&h=149ff238&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pjNom1K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpjNom1K.png&h=853a3001&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m64qAmL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm64qAmL.png&h=3e7d2cc1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n依家我想整大量語錄俾大家對付藍絲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但問題嚟喇<br />\n我唔肯定係邊個講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以幫幫我，搵番講果句說話果條友出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n方便我整圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760baee9ced42e72090f87e6a162630c9c9706ae","tid":1470611,"uid":49833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:03:00.000Z","msg":"多謝原po #290 你講我聽巴打嘅整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>現階段仲係調查當中 唔係可妄下評論<br />\n<br />\n我手頭上無呢啲資料 唔敢作實答你<br />\n<br />\n佢唔係現場出現就冇事 去得果度就可能有呢啲風險<br />\n<br />\n做法不完美，但可接受，要改善<br />\n<br />\n而家眾說紛云，我認為事主可以去報警先，警方必定會跟進調查<br />\n<br />\n在場嘅市民只係用最低武力，當一切平靜後，真誠對話就會展開<br />\n<br />\n歡迎提供證據</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a12df918d04afd3b371a15b898bd4dae35d22e9a","tid":1470611,"uid":49833,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:05:39.000Z","msg":"仲有原po#692 移除下體裝置嘅整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>實際情況同影片所見未必一樣<br />\n<br />\n示威者表現克制，不存在過度武力，雖不完美，仍有改進空間。<br />\n<br />\n現未能掌握足夠資料，有關人士願意提供資料會好樂意。<br />\n<br />\n疑似示威者用嘅係疑似拳頭接觸疑似環球日報記者， 片段質素實在太差， 大家要搜習更多證據，先可以下判斷<br />\n<br />\n無有關資訊喺手<br />\n<br />\n自己並非「彈藥專家」不清楚催淚彈過期會否失效或對人體造成傷害。<br />\n<br />\n使用催淚彈有既定程序及嚴格規管的指引，不會構成人身安全問題，<br />\n<br />\n現階段仲係調查當中 唔係可妄下評論<br />\n<br />\n我手頭上無呢啲資料 唔敢作實答你<br />\n<br />\n佢唔係現場出現就冇事 去得果度就可能有呢啲風險<br />\n<br />\n做法不完美，但可接受，要改善<br />\n<br />\n而家眾說紛云，我認為事主可以去報警先，警方必定會跟進調查<br />\n<br />\n在場嘅市民只係用最低武力，當一切平靜後，真誠對話就會展開<br />\n<br />\n電光火石之間 前線人員難免要即刻做出啲非常決定<br />\n<br />\n香港人沒學過抗爭 難免掌握不好<br />\n<br />\n至於個別事件我需要返去做一個詳細嘅調查先可以答到你<br />\n<br />\n確實時間就...我只可以答你盡快<br />\n<br />\n這一種是仇視 是對立的心態 對香港完全沒有好處 <br />\n<br />\n暫時手頭無資料 你問番記者先知<br />\n<br />\n改一改啲字就用得，大家補充一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a2bbec94408d85d14995fd4443a3926fd7ace898","tid":1470611,"uid":141176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a664a5007cb70f00d80089fd9398204a9c07d5be","tid":1470611,"uid":8584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:05:53.000Z","msg":"幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd0e44e0d7e5ff8c779d8353c1f612038359768","tid":1470611,"uid":232229,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:06:54.000Z","msg":"要整埋sticker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9687f010ca405ef52705c9b9e4b7177b48ff62a0","tid":1470611,"uid":49833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote